title: The Beatles - She Loves You [Drop In, Stockholm, 1963] (Blu-ray)
description:
The Beatles - She Loves You [Drop In, Stockholm, 1963] (Blu-ray).m2ts


HQ rare live performance music video from a promo Blu-ray. 
Despite having completed their concert tour of Sweden the night before, The Beatles returned to Stockholm to record an appearance on the Sveriges Television music show Drop In.
(video does not have any logos)
